Package org.anchoranalysis.image.io.stack.input

Non-bean classes for reading a Stack from the filesystem.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OpenedRaster
    A raster-image that has been opened for reading containing one or more series of image-Stacks.
    ProvidesStackInput
    Base class for inputs which somehow eventually send up providing stacks, with or without names
    StackSequenceInput
    Provides a single stack (or a time series of such stacks) as an input
    TimeSequenceSupplier  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MaskReader
    Utility functions for reading a Mask from the file-system.
    StackInputInitParamsCreator  
    TileRasters
